Citation.sTitle: Solubilities of 1,1'-(Propane-1,3-diyl)-bis(pyridinium) Dihexafluorophosphate in Dimethyl Sulfoxide + Water
Citation.sAbstract: The solubilities of 1,1'-(propane-1,3-diyl)-bis(pyridinium) dihexafluorophosphate in dimethyl sulfoxide + water were measured at temperatures from (290.45 to 337.05) K by a laser monitoring observation technique at atmospheric pressure. The experimental data were correlated with the modified Apelblat equation.
